#

Tomato and Mozzarella Panini

15 min
$5.5
450 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 1

Allergens:

GlutenDairy

Dietary Tags:

Vegetarian

Cuisine:

Italian

Course:

Main

Tags:

EasyQuickVegetarian

Description

A deliciously melty panini filled with fresh tomatoes and creamy mozzarella cheese, toasted to perfection.

Ingredients

  • ciabatta bread: 2 slices
  • fresh mozzarella cheese: 4 ounces
  • tomato: 1 large, sliced
  • fresh basil leaves: a handful
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • balsamic glaze: 1 teaspoon
